Participating in peer review is optional but highly encouraged, and is the primary expected way to earn points toward your {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://gatech.instructure.com/courses/498210/assignments/2344398"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 class participation grade}}. To participate in peer review, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://gatech.instructure.com/courses/498210/assignments/2351462"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 submit to the separate peer review assignment}} in Canvas to share your assignment with peers and receive assignments to review in turn. Review the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://gatech.instructure.com/courses/498210/pages/primer-on-peer-review"}}{\fldrslt \cf5 \ul \ulc5 Primer on Peer Review page}} for more details.\
